Letter 'n'


Problem Description:

Find all the employees whose first name ends with the letter 'n'.

Return the columns 'employee_id', 'full_name' (first name and last name separated by space), and 'phone_number'.
Use the employees table.
Dataset Description:

https://d2beiqkhq929f0.cloudfront.net/public_assets/assets/000/004/944/original/hr_img.PNG?1653046505


Solution:


SELECT employee_id, concat(first_name, ' ', last_name) as full_name, phone_number
FROM employees
where first_name like '%n'
